red to sign and be photographed at the counter of\nthe State Administration for Market Regulation. If the\nnatural person is overseas, he/she is required to apply\nfor notarisation or a notarised certification document\nof his/her identity at a qualified law firm overseas. If\nthe document is not in Chinese, a translation must be\nprovided.\nIf the investor is a foreign enterprise, the notarisation\nor notarised document of the enterprise must be done\nat a local law firm; if the document is not in Chinese, a\ntranslation must be provided.\nOverseas natural\nperson\nForeign enterprise\n1\n2\n\n## Page 9\n\nGoGBA go-to guide\nSetting up a business in the Greater Bay Area (I) - Business registration and business/investment filing\n9\nNotes for foreign investors\nbefore investment\n3\nForeign investors should first determine whether their investment project\nis categorised as restricted, prohibited or encouraged. Encouraged\ninvestment shall also refer to relevant incentive policies.\nThe establishment of FIEs mainly includes registration and record filing procedures with the Administration\nof Industry and Commerce and the Ministry of Commerce. Policies including “five certificates in one”, “one\nlicence, one code” and “one-window processing” have been launched to simplify the procedures.\nThe mainland prohibits FIEs to invest or establish enterprises in certain industries listed in the “Special\nAdministrative Measures (Negative List) for Foreign Investment Access (2021 edition)” and “Special\nAdministrative Measures (Negative List) for the Access of Foreign Investment in Pilot Free Trade Zones (2021)”.\n1\n3\n4\n2\nEnterprise self-declaration\nWithin the\n“Negative List”\nSubject to approval\nApproval documents\nobtained from the\nin-charge Bureau of\nCommerce\nOutside the\n“Negative List”\nRecord filing\nprocedures completed\nComparison with the\n“Negative List”\nIndustrial or commercial\nregistration (obtaining licence)\nFive-in-one licence filing\ninformation reporting system\n(for tax registration, etc)", "content_hash": "760c0bcd8465", "chapter": null, "section": null, "page": "8"}
