me may vary depending on the actual circumstances.\n\nThe Bank reserves the right to request any relevant supporting documents/information from the customer.\n\nPromotion period is from 1 January 2026 to 31 March 2026 (both dates inclusive).\n\nThis product is applicable to corporate with 2 years or above business operation.\n\nThe above products, services and offers are subject to the relevant terms and conditions.\n\nThe Bank reserves the rights to amend, suspend and terminate the above products and services and to amend the relevant terms at any time at its sole discretion without prior notice.\n\nIn case of any dispute, the decision of the Bank shall be final.\n\nShould there be any discrepancy between the Chinese and English versions of this webpage, the Chinese version shall prevail.\n\nMake an Application Now\n\nPrint\n\nQuick Link\n\nAccount Services\n\nLoan\n\nService Charges\n\nOnline Loan Application\n\nService Charges\n\nCorporate Customer Service\n\nHotline +852 3988 2288\n\nBranch Locator\n\nen", "content_hash": "96702a22831f", "chapter": null, "section": null, "page": null}
