and including the Valuation Date in accordance with the General Terms and Conditions. Changes in the market price of\nany Linked Stock may not lead to a corresponding change, or any change at all, in the market value of, and/or your potential gain or loss under,\nour Basket ELIs.", "content_hash": "a8c320d6da55", "chapter": null, "section": null, "page": null}
