n\nOn the View menu, select Zoom, then Zoom In.\n\nOr you may click on the Menu icon and select + or - to make the text size bigger or smaller.\n\nInternet Explorer / Edge\n\nOn the View menu, select Text Size, then Largest.\n\nOr you may click on the IE Settings icon, select Zoom, then choose a percentage or click Zoom In.\n\nOpera\n\nOn the View menu, select Zoom. Then choose a percentage.\n\nSafari\n\nOn the View menu, select Make Text Bigger.\n\nEndorsement Disclaimer\n\nCR does not endorse specific web browsers or recommend one browser over another. While some popular browsers are included here, mention of a specific browser does not imply any endorsement or recommendation.\n\nAbout us\n\nBack\n\nAbout us\n\nOur Registry\nupdated\n\nBack\n\nOur Registry\nupdated\n\nWelcome Message\n\nVision and Mission\n\nRole of the Companies Registry\n\nOrganisation & Distribution of Business\nupdated\n\nOrdinances Administered\n\nPerformance Pledges\nupdated\n\nCustomer Service Survey\nupdated\n\nCorporate Social Responsibility\n\nCorporate Governance\n\n繁 | 簡 |\n\nWhat's New\nnew\n\nEvents\nupdated\n\nVolunteer Works\nnew\n\nConsolidated Annual Open Data Plans (Spatial Data Plans included)\nnew\n\nInformation for Persons of Different Races\nupdated\n\nContact Us\nupdated\n\nBack\n\nContact Us\nupdated\n\nWhere We Are\n\nEnquiries, Complaints & Suggestions\nupdated\n\nAccess Co-ordinator and Access Officers\nupdated\n\n繁 | 簡 |\n\nMajor Services\n\nBack\n\nMajor Services\n\nHow to register a new company?\n\nHow to change a company name?\n\nWhat are the general filing requirements?\n\nHow to obtain company information?\nupdated\n\nHow to deregister a defunct solvent company?\n\nMajor Fees under the Companies Ordinance\nupdated\n\nLicensing of Money Lenders\nupdated\n\nBack\n\nLicensing of Money Lenders\nupdated\n\nInformation for Licensed Money Lenders\nnew\n\nInformation for Borrowers / Intending Borrowers\nnew\n\n繁 | 簡 |\n\nForms\n\nBack\n\nForms\n\nSpecified Forms\nupdated\