s, data breaches and identity theft.\n\nRead more\n\nRelated Video:\n\nMag-ingat sa fraud at scam\n\nLoan Calculator\n\nThe loan calculator will help financial consumers shop for the best loan product that banks offer as may be suitable for their needs.\n\nRead more\n\nConsumer Assistance Channels of BSP Supervised Institutions\n\nEconomic and Financial Education\n\nEconomic and Financial Education: Overview\n\nEconomic and Financial Education Partnerships\n\nLearning Resources\n\nLearning Events\n\nCampaigns\n\nPisoLit and EkoLit\n\nKnowledge Resource Network\n\nContact us\n\nPERA (Personal Equity and Retirement Account)\n\nOverview of Personal Equity and Retirement Account (PERA)\n\nIntroduction\n\nFAQs\n\nPERA FAQs\n\nFAQs on Tax Credit for the PERA Contributions\n\nMultimedia\n\nLaunch of Digital PERA\n\nDigital PERA Launch Highlights\n\nAno ang Digital PERA?\n\nPERA Laws, Rules and Regulations\n\nRA 9505 (PERA Act of 2008)\n\n2009 PERA Implementing Rules and Regulations (IRR)\n\n2019 IRR Amendment\n\n2023 IRR Amendment\n\nBSP PERA Issuances\n\nPERA Tax Regulations\n\nPERA Events and Publications\n\nPublications\n\nEvents\n\nDigital PERA Platforms and Directory of Market Participants\n\nDirectory of Market Participants\n\nStatistics\n\nQuarterly Statistics\n\nReminders on Investing\n\nBasic Reminders\n\nInvesting Tips\n\nLegal\n\nBSP Privacy Policy\n\nTerms of Use\n\nAbbreviations and Glossary\n\nSite Map\n\nQuick Links\n\nCareers\n\nBSP Directory\n\nFeedback\n\nNew Order of Payment System (NOPS)\n\n© 2025 BANGKO SENTRAL NG PILIPINAS - All Rights Reserved", "content_hash": "3e08407753d2", "chapter": null, "section": null, "page": null}
