{"doc_id": "sbv_circular_15_2024_payment_services", "parent_doc_id": "sbv_circular_15_2024_payment_services", "title": "Press release on issuance of Circular No. 15/2024/TT-NHNN", "issuer": "State Bank of Vietnam", "authority_level": "central_bank", "region": ["Vietnam"], "topic": ["payment systems", "payment services", "foreign exchange regulation"], "region_code": "VN", "topic_code": "remittance", "source_url": "https://www.sbv.gov.vn/en/web/sbv_portal/w/press-release-on-issuance-of-circular-no.-15/2024/tt-nhnn", "document_url": "", "source_type": "HTML", "language": "en", "demo_relevance": "high", "publish_date": "2024-06-28", "effective_date": "", "trust_tier": "central_bank", "document_type": "circular", "chunk_id": "sbv_circular_15_2024_payment_services__c0000", "chunk_index": 0, "char_start": 0, "char_end": 2965, "content": "# Press release on issuance of Circular No. 15/2024/TT-NHNN\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 15/2024/TT-NHNN\n\n03/07/2024 22:51:00\n\n0:00\n\n/\n\n0:00\n\nGiọng Nam\n\nGiọng Nữ\n\nPress releas e on issuance of Circular No. 15/2024/TT-NHNN\n\nOn June 28, 2024, the Governor of the State Bank of Vietnam (SBV) issued Circular No. 15/2024/TT-NHNN regulating the provision of non-cash payment services .\n\nThis Circular is composed of 04 Chapters with 23 Articles, specifically as follows:\n\nChapter 1: General provisions, comprising of 6 Articles ( from Article 1 to Article 6), stipulating the scope of regulation; the subjects of application ; the interpretation of some terms; the payment documents; the payment services by e lectronic means; the corrective and adjustment procedures for errors, the review and handling of complaints in payment transactions and intermediary payment services.\n\nChapter 2: Payment services via payment service providers, comprising of 9 Articles ( from Article 7 to Article 15) , regulating the single payment transactions via p ayment accounts opened at the SBV ; authorized payment and authorized collection services; money transfer services , etc.\n\nChapter 3 : Rights and r esponsibilities of the pa r ties, comprising of 6 Articles (from Article 16 to Article 21) regulating the rights and responsibi li ties of the payment service providers and the service users; the rights and responsibilities of the payment service providers when cooperating with payment intermediary service providers, international institutions, payment acceptance units; the rights and responsibilities of payment acceptance units.\n\nChapter 4: Enforcement, comprising of 2 Articles (Article 22 and Article 23) regulating the implementation arrangements, and the enforcement\n\nThis new Circular takes effe ct form July 1, 2024.\n\nHY\n\naA\n\nCategories:\n\nOther Press Releases\n\nOTHER NEWS\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 20/2026/TT-NHNN\n\n05/02/2028\n\nPress Release on issuance of Circular No.09/2026/TT-NHNN\n\n05/10/2027\n\nPress Release on issuance of Circular No.08/2026/TT-NHNN\n\n05/07/2027\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 04/2026/TT-NHNN\n\n04/08/2027\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 60/2025/TT-NHNN\n\n01/12/2026\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 51/2025/TT-NHNN\n\n01/12/2026\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 83/2025/TT-NHNN\n\n02/12/2026\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 85/2025/TT-NHNN\n\n01/05/2028\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 82/2025/TT-NHNN\n\n01/05/2028\n\nPress release on issuance of Circular No. 81/2025/TT-NHNN\n\n01/10/2027\n\nShowing 1 to 10 of 491\n\n1\n\n2\n\n3\n\n...\n\n50\n\nAbout SBV\n\nHistory\n\nMajor Responsibilities\n\nManagement Board\n\nFormer Governors\n\nCPI\n\nReserve requirement\n\nInterest Rate\n\nMoney Market Operations\n\nNotification of New Offering off the State Bank Bills\n\nInvitation for Gold Auctions\n\nNghiệp vụ thị trường mở\n\nĐấu thầu Tín phiếu kho bạc nhà nước\n\nSystem of Credit Institutions\n\nBanks", "content_hash": "ffcac71118db", "chapter": "1", "section": null, "