{"doc_id": "hkmc_sfgs_application_procedures", "parent_doc_id": "hkmc_sfgs_application_procedures", "title": "SME Financing Guarantee Scheme Application Procedures", "issuer": "HKMC Insurance Limited", "authority_level": "official_dev", "region": ["Hong Kong"], "topic": ["SME loan", "financing guarantee", "eligibility"], "region_code": "HK", "topic_code": "credit", "source_url": "https://www.hkmc.com.hk/files/product_file/6/1051/SFGS%20Application%20Procedures%20202004_Eng.pdf", "document_url": "", "source_type": "PDF", "language": "en", "demo_relevance": "high", "publish_date": "2020-04-01", "effective_date": "", "trust_tier": "official_dev", "document_type": "unknown", "chunk_id": "hkmc_sfgs_application_procedures__c0000", "chunk_index": 0, "char_start": 0, "char_end": 2078, "content": "# SME Financing Guarantee Scheme Application Procedures\n\n## Page 1\n\nSME Financing Guarantee Scheme (SFGS)\n\nApplication Procedures\n\nStep 1 – Application\nThe participating Lende r (“PL”) assesses the application of the\nBorrower and, if the PL supports the application, it completes the\napplication forms with the Borrower. The PL submits the duly\nsigned application forms, a copy of the proposed facility letterNote 1 and\nall necessa ry supporting documents to HKMC Insurance Limited\n(“HKMCI”).\nStep 2 – Approval and issuance of Guarantee\nIf the application is approved, all the\napplication form(s) are duly completed and\nsigned and supporting doc uments are\nprovided to the satisfaction of the HKMC I,\nthe HKMCI issues a Guarantee to the PL by\naround 3 business days in general.\nLast Step – Guarantee Fee Payment and Effective of GuaranteeNote 2\nThe PL collects the guarantee fee and remits to the HKMC. In the event that the\nSingle Upfront guarantee fee is financed by the PL, the PL deducts the guarantee\nfee from the loan proceeds for remitting to the HKMC.\nThe relevant Guarantee in favour of the PL will take effect only until the guarantee\nfee is received by the HKMC.\n\nStep 2 – Approval-in-Principle\nThe HKMCI issues a Notification of Result to\nthe PL by around 3 business days in general.\nIf the applicat ion is approved by the\nHKMCI, the PL prepares necessary\ndocuments for the borrower to sign and\naccept.\n\nStraight-Through Approval Route Normal Approval Route\nStep 3 – Confirmation and issuance of\nGuarantee\nThe PL submits the signed documents and\nnecessary supporting documents to the\nHKMCI for the issuance of the\nGuarantee by\naround 2 business days in general.\n04/2020 P. 1/2\n\n## Page 2\n\nSME Financing Guarantee Scheme (SFGS)\n\nApplication Procedures\n\nNotes\n1. Submission of facility letter is not required for the Special 100% Loan\nGuarantee.\n2. Last Step is not applicable to the Special 100% Loan Guarantee.\n\nRemarks\n\nThe SME Financing Guarantee Scheme is operated by the HKMCI. The copyright\nto the contents of this document is owned by the HKMCI.\n04/2020 P. 2/2", "content_hash": "50009ae1f240", "chapter": null, "section": null, "page": "1"}
